{"word":"κατασκέλλομαι","slug":"κατασκέλλομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατασκέλλομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>κατέσκληκα</el> ) (plup. <el>κατεσκλήκει</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to become a skeleton, wither</i> or <i>pine away</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—so in <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>κατέσκληκα</el> and plup. <el>κατεσκλήκει</el>, <b><a href='S:Babrius'>Babr.</a></b><p/>"}]}